<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>AI Risk Assessment</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; }
    label { font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; display: block; }
    select, button { width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div><strong><h1>AI Risk Assessment</h1></strong></div>
<div style="margin-bottom: 18px;">
  <p>
    This tool evaluates the risk of an AI system using principles from the AIRO Ontology. It collects AI risk inputs via a structured questionnaire, applies heuristic risk scoring logic, and outputs results as a human-readable Markdown report and RDF/Turtle data for linked data applications. Available as both a web app and CLI tool.
  </p>
</div>
  </header>
  <form action="/submit" method="post">
    <% @allowed.each do |key, values| %>
      <label><%= key.to_s.capitalize %></label>
      <select name="<%= key %>" required>
        <% values.each do |v| %>
          <option value="<%= v %>"><%= v %></option>
        <% end %>
      </select>
    <% end %>
    <br>
    <button type="submit">Submit Assessment</button>
  </form>
  <footer style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 16px 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; text-align: center; font-size: 0.95em; color: #555;">

    <div>
      <a href="https://github.com/inloopstudio/AI-Risk-Ontology-AIRO" target="_blank">GitHub Project</a> &mdash; Sponsored by <a href="https://inloop.studio/?utm_source=ai-risk-tool&utm_medium=web&utm_campaign=footer-link" target="_blank">inloop.studio</a>
    </div>
    <div><small style="color: #888;">This is an experimental project.</small></div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
